{"tid":122640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"維生素片竟致癌！科學家揭露這個百年來的殘酷營銷騙局","createTime":"2017-02-16T07:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T08:02:54.000Z","uid":72226,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa53956d8b0fb1639225ac61c8d723d7e6a77203","tid":122640,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:47:32.000Z","msg":"總結了各種研究成果之後，我們可以知道：對於患有特定疾病的人來說維生素確實可以幫助治療疾病。但是對於我們普通人來說，服用維生素片收效甚微甚至伴有致癌等副作用，而且一旦服用過量，還會導致維生素中毒等。<br />\n<br />\n因此，對於我們普通人來說除非你已經出現了明顯的缺乏維生素的癥狀，否則還是不要吃維生素片為好。"},{"pid":"a76103e287ae10d260d240682c349950d2f4adad","tid":122640,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.golden-ages.org/2017/01/20/20170120-01/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.golden-ages.org%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F20170120-01%2F&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c6dd72f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.golden-ages.org/2017/01/20/20170120-01/</a><br />\n<br />\n呢排仲乜咁多fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495cd6fda5a4267d700d0429502bfef87f5371a2","tid":122640,"uid":9053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"素你老母<br />\n<br />\n我淨係識維他命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456f807c4be1f2ec6debd8463ca44b2f14dd2aef","tid":122640,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>素你老母<br />\n<br />\n我淨係識維他命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又唔係我話 <br />\n篇fake news話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鬼唔知叫維他命咩"}]}